OL,5, Sir Keir Starmer has called on Liz     
OL,6, Truss not to claim an allowance of up  
OL,7, to #115,000 a year that she would be   
OL,8, entitled to after resigning as PM.     
OL,10,FLiz Truss announced her resignation    
OL,11,Ffrom the lectern outside No 10 on      
OL,12,FThursday after just 44 days in the job.
OL,14,FIt means she will now be able to claim 
OL,15,Fthe Public Duty Costs Allowance (PDCA),
OL,16,Fcurrently set at #115,000, which all   
OL,17,Fformer prime ministers are entitled to.
OL,19,FBut the Labour leader said she's "not  
OL,20,Fearned the right" to the entitlement.  
